0.85;\">Our ethical guidelines for persuasive content design.</p><a href=\"https://slideforge.dev/ethics\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 16px 40px; background: #C2B860; color: #020200; font-family: Plus Jakarta Sans; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 9999px; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px #52460040; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin: 0 0 14px;\">Study the Framework</a><div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#CFCEC3;margin-top:2px;opacity:0.85;letter-spacing:0.02em;\">\ud83d\udd17 github.com/ishan-parihar/slideforge-rust</div></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
